Package: metSim
Type: Package
Title: Simulation of Multi-Environment Trial (MET) Networks and Model Comparison
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Marcos", "Filho", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "you@example.com")
Description: Tools to simulate multi-environment breeding trials (MET) with a
    known ground truth and to compare genotype-by-environment (GxE) models
    (main effect, compound symmetry, factor-analytic and others) fitted with
    'ASReml-R'. Beta release, in active development.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/marcos100110/metSim
BugReports: https://github.com/marcos100110/metSim/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: MASS, Matrix, dplyr, tidyr, ggplot2, sn
Suggests: asreml
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
